RELEASE OF LIEN BOND
Revised Executed Original Bond
BOND NO . 0780900
KNOW ALL MEN BY THESE PRESENTS, that we, 1200 Howell Street, LLC
as Principal, and Harco National Insurance Company
as Surety, are held
and firmly bound unto Skanska USA Building Inc.
as Obligee, in the sum of
Sixty-six Thousand Nine Hundred Fifty-three And No/100THS
( $66,953.00
Dollars, lawful money of the United States of America, to the payment of
which, well and truly to be paid, we bind ourselves, our heirs, executors and
successors, jointly and severally, firmly by these presents.
THE CONDITION OF THE ABOVE OBLIGATION IS SUCH, That WHEREAS,
Skanska USA Building Inc.
Unofficial Copy
is the claimant under that certain
mechanic's lien No. 20200714001089 *
in the amount of
Forty-four Thousand Six Hundred Thirty-four and 91/100
Dollars ($44,634.91
recorded on 7/14/2020 , in the office of the County Recorder of King County
State of Washington, with respect to property of the 1200 Howell Street, LLC
Located at Assessor's Property Tax Parcel No .: 607550-1620, Nexus Condominium Unit 1801
* Amending Lien Nos. 20200131002276 and 20200210000017
WHEREAS, said Principal disputes the correctness or validity of such claim of
lien and desires to execute and record a bond pursuant to the provisions of
RCW 60.04 of the State of Washington to enable the real property above
described to be freed from the effect of said claim of lien and any action
brought to foreclosed said lien.
NOW, THEREFORE, THE CONDITION OF THIS OBLIGATION IS SUCH, That, if the
Principal shall pay any sum which claimant may recover on said claim, together
with his costs of suit in the action, if he recovers therein, then this
obligation shall be void; otherwise to remain in full force and effect.
Signed, sealed and dated this _13th
day of October
2021
